---
title: Spicy Falafel Wraps with Pickled Jalapeños and Creamy Avocado Tahini
description: A filling and delicious handheld dinner is on your bingo card this week! These herbaceous chickpea patties are met with tangy pickled veggies, as well as a bright avocado-tahini sauce before being wrapped in toasty flatbread.
